title: Ratty Matty - Create Your Vision - The Ship
description:
Tattoo artist Ratty Matty gives us a look over his shoulder as he draws up a pirate ship in the American Traditional style at his Newport Beach studio. 

Arnette Eyewear is the lens through which artists create their vision. Matty wears the Holly in matte black (Rhythm in translucent red also pictured) find yours at http://www.arnette.com

Band: Rustangs
Song: We Can Leave The Cops Out Of It
